any datatype -> This variable accepts any type of data type 
unknown datatype -> this variable accepts any data type in 

differents any and unknown

In any data type we can access methods 

but unknown data type we can't access methods


example:
        let a:any = 5;
        let b:unknown = 2;
        
        a="hi"
        b="bye"

        a.toUpperCase()//we can access toUpperCase method
        b.toUpperCase()//we can'nt access toUpperCase method